Final .gitignore can look like this:

# Playwright
node_modules/
/test-results/
/playwright-report/
/blob-report/
/playwright/.cache/
/playwright/.auth/

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db